11
00:03:01,400 --> 00:03:02,280
One hundred million

12
00:03:02,360 --> 00:03:03,880
in exchange for your wife's life.

13
00:03:17,880 --> 00:03:19,200
It's medicine from Indhorn.

14
00:03:33,360 --> 00:03:35,320
The workers who caught the virus

15
00:03:35,400 --> 00:03:37,840
