18
00:03:57,160 --> 00:03:58,320
Let me handle him, Rin.

19
00:04:01,560 --> 00:04:03,480
You know how long
I've been waiting for this.

20
00:04:04,040 --> 00:04:05,280
I've put up with so much.

21
00:04:05,960 --> 00:04:09,840
I know, but the only thing I want…

22
00:04:15,280 --> 00:04:16,720
is for you to stay alive.

23
00:04:21,079 --> 00:04:24,240
So I have to let the guy
who murdered my father live an evil life

24
00:04:24,320 --> 00:04:25,320
and harm people?

25
00:04:27,240 --> 00:04:28,800
I'd rather die.

26
00:04:30,520 --> 00:04:32,880
If you don't truly understand my pain,

27
00:04:34,000 --> 00:04:35,960
quit trying to stop me.

28
00:04:39,080 --> 00:04:41,360
I'd rather die with pride

29
00:04:41,440 --> 00:04:44,160
than live a half-assed life, Taiga.

