Have you found her?

48
00:07:57,920 --> 00:07:59,840
Where is Punlop hiding your mom?

49
00:07:59,920 --> 00:08:02,280
The detectives are tracking her down, Dad.

50
00:08:02,880 --> 00:08:04,080
Find her as soon as possible.

51
00:08:05,040 --> 00:08:08,240
No matter how many people
or how much money it takes, pay them.

52
00:08:09,120 --> 00:08:10,120
Okay, Dad.

53
