54
00:08:28,440 --> 00:08:30,880
It contains all the videos
related to Fire Phoenix,

55
00:08:32,799 --> 00:08:35,559
the list of people he bribed,

56
00:08:36,840 --> 00:08:39,159
and his secret bank account overseas.

57
00:08:40,960 --> 00:08:42,240
What about its PIN?

58
00:08:43,240 --> 00:08:44,200
That too.

59
00:08:46,400 --> 00:08:47,880
Don't leak the story of Ratee's dad,

60
00:08:48,960 --> 00:08:51,600
then I'll make all the evidence
against you disappear.

61
00:08:57,200 --> 00:08:58,320
Don't cross me.

62
00:09:00,680 --> 00:09:04,000
If I die and don't
get out of here in an hour,

63
00:09:04,960 --> 00:09:07,480
your pictures will be uploaded
to every page.

64
00:09:08,720 --> 00:09:10,520
But if we can come to an agreement,

65
00:09:12,480 --> 00:09:13,680
we'll go our separate ways.

66
00:09:14,520 --> 00:09:16,800
We'll get out of here together…

67
00:09:18,920 --> 00:09:21,200
after I've gotten the money from Naruban.

68
00:09:25,080 --> 00:09:26,040
Do it.

69
00:09:27,040 --> 00:09:29,120
Send Naruban's money
to the account I opened.

70
00:09:30,680 --> 00:09:31,760
Now.

71
00:09:46,200 --> 00:09:49,600
WE DETECTED AN ATTEMPT TO ACCESS
YOUR ACCOUNT. ID VERIFICATION REQUIRED

72
